    <p>Anhui Northen Imp. & Exp. Co., Ltd was established in 2009 , formerly Beautiful Life
        Porcelain Co., Ltd. , mainly engaged in the export of all kinds of arts & craft gifts ,
        including ceramic crafts, resin crafts, crystal crafts, glass crafts, bamboo crafts ,
        and handmade crafts. Products range from garden supplies& decorations, home decoration
        to gifts& crafts for special occasions.</p>

    <p>The company has been shooting up since its foundation, and has cooperated with many clients
        mainly from Europe, America and Oceania etc. The core spirit of the company is "Quality Products
        and Professional Service", aiming to building a good and long-term partnership with
        customers.With the abundant experience in international trade, reliable teamwork spirit and
        strict QC system, our products and services have garnered various acclaim from the customers all
        over the world.</p>

    <p>Nowadays, with the advanced management and a professional team, our products enjoy a good
        reputation among our clients globally. We have our own production enterprise and fine cooperated
        factories, OEM is the line that we are especially specialized in now. Businessmen home and
        abroad are warmly welcome to visit us. We sincerely hope you would join us and share the most
        mutual benefits soon. </p>

